---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Resources" description="Places to find support when you need it.">
  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Resources</h1>
    <p class="tagline">Places to find support.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="container">
    <p class="lead">
      Inner work can surface things that are tender or difficult.<br />
      If you need support, these are good places to start.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <h2>Crisis Support</h2>
    <p>If you're in immediate distress, please reach out:</p>
    <ul class="resource-list">
      <li>
        <strong>988 Suicide & Crisis Lifeline</strong> (US)<br />
        Call or text <a href="tel:988">988</a> â€” available 24/7
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Crisis Text Line</strong><br />
        Text <strong>HOME</strong> to <a href="sms:741741">741741</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>International Association for Suicide Prevention</strong><br />
        <a href="https://www.iasp.info/resources/Crisis_Centres/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Find a crisis center in your country</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <h2>Finding a Therapist</h2>
    <p>If you're looking for ongoing professional support:</p>
    <ul class="resource-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Psychology Today Therapist Finder</strong><br />
        <a href="https://www.psychologytoday.com/us/therapists" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Search by location, specialty, and insurance</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Open Path Collective</strong><br />
        <a href="https://openpathcollective.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Affordable therapy ($30-$80/session)</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Inclusive Therapists</strong><br />
        <a href="https://www.inclusivetherapists.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Directory centered on marginalized communities</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <h2>Peer Support</h2>
    <p>Sometimes you just need to talk to someone who understands:</p>
    <ul class="resource-list">
      <li>
        <strong>Warmlines</strong> (non-crisis support)<br />
        <a href="https://warmline.org/warmdir.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Find a warmline in your state</a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>7 Cups</strong><br />
        <a href="https://www.7cups.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Free online chat with trained listeners</a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <section class="container">
    <p class="closing">
      Reaching out is not weakness. It's wisdom.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .lead {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .resource-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .resource-list li {
    padding: var(--space-md);
    border-left: 2px solid var(--accent-subtle);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .resource-list li strong {
    color: var(--text-primary);
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .resource-list a {
    color: var(--accent-warm);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .resource-list a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-glow);
  }

  .closing {
    text-align: center;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-top: var(--space-lg);
  }
</style>
